  <brief_title>hATG+CsA vs hATG+CsA+Eltrombopag for SAA</brief_title>
  <acronym>RACE</acronym>
  <official_title>A Prospective Randomized Multicenter Study Comparing Horse Antithymocyte Globuline (hATG) + Cyclosporine A (CsA) With or Without Eltrombopag as Front-line Therapy for Severe Aplastic Anemia Patients.</official_title>
